    <section id="ecommerce_persona1">
        <div class="container-fluid p-l-0 p-r-0">
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="persona-content col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">MICRO BUSINESS OWNER</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Tessy Wang</h4>
                    <p>Tessy loves scented candles. That’s how she came up with the idea of running an online business selling scented candles. But not any type of candles. She wanted to build a product that would reflect her values. Soy made candles, hand
                        poured in the USA in small batches, with a distinctive fragrance.
                        <p>
                            <p>She also wanted to build a community around the product. That’s why she connected with candle lovers on Instagram. They participated in giving their ideas and testing her products. Tessy came up with three fragrances - Serenity,
                                Boldness and Clarity. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/project-candle.png" alt="Illustration of three candles burning with soybeans in front of them."></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/project-box.png" alt="Illustration of three minimalist brown boxes made of recycled material with white strip on the top."></div>
                <div
                    class="persona-content col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">PRODUCT DESIGN</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Scented candles</h4>
                    <p>Tessy follows the minimalist movement in design - reducing the products to their simplest form or essential nature. That’s how, she says, she designed the glass container and the signature box. </p>
                    <p>But that’s not all. She and her community are eco-conscious. That’s why her signature boxes are made of recycled paper, and her labels from recycled coffee bags.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
            <div class="persona-content col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <h6 class="text-boja">SALE CHANNELS</h6>
                <h4 class="text-boja">E-commerce</h4>
                <p>Tessy started her business on Amazon. Pretty soon, she needed to make a Web site that would be a one stop shop for her Amazon and Instagram accounts.
                    <p>
                        <p>She found two freelancers on Fiver.</p>
                        <p>“It was a disaster,” says Tessy. “They over promised and under delivered.”</p>
                        <p>She didn’t want to use WordPress as a CMS, but they convinced her it was the best choice. They didn’t know anything about design, so she had to step in and make design decisions. They seem not to know about development either,
                            since they didn’t implement many functionalities. Her Web site to this day is not a finished product.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/negativereviews.png" alt="Illustration of tired small business owner slump in a chair with her head on a computer keayboard.">                </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
            <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/project-negative-reviews.png" alt="Illustration of three candles burning in the middle. Angry customers all around."></div>
            <div
                class="persona-content col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <h6 class="text-boja">SUPPLIERS</h6>
                <h4 class="text-boja">Negative reviews</h4>
                <p>But that wasn’t the end to her troubles. Her suppliers didn’t send her the product for final testing, so she had a rude awakening on Amazon. Her glowing 5 star reviews suddenly went to a 1 star reviews. Her customers complained that her
                    scented candles smelled like a Dove soap or hygienic products.</p>
                <p>When she finally got the product for testing, she realized that suppliers replaced the fragrance.</p>
                <p>As a result, she is now out of stock. On top of that, she has to order boxes from China, although she was adamant about using only US made supplies.</p>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
            <div class="persona-content col-xl-6">
                <h6 class="text-boja">PSYCHOLOGY</h6>
                <h4 class="text-boja">Stressful life event</h4>
                <p>Tessy is a young mother. Her baby needs constant attention and her business troubles started affecting her wellbeing.
                    <p>
                        <p>But she is not giving up yet. She decided to finally have an e-commerce Web site, that would help her automate her business, and handle all concerns on the go. She also found another supplier and hope to build a lasting relationship
                            with them.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/majkastress.png" alt="Illustration of a mother holding a baby in her arms with a thinking bubble above her head - one candle burning in the thinking bubble.">                </div>
        </div>
        </div>
