            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="persona-content col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">SCENTED CANDLES LOVER</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Billy McKenzie</h4>
                    <p>Billy McKenzie loves scented candles. She buys a different fragrance for each room.</p>
                    <p>She places mint and lavender in the bedroom, an evergreen and woodsy candle in the living room, and amber and vanilla in the kitchen.
                        <p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/candlesinrooms.png" alt="Illustrations of three candles; one surrounded by lavander flowers, one surrounded by evergreen leaves, one surrounded with amber and vanilla."></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/stockpile.png" alt="Illustration of different kind of candles stockpile on shelves."></div>
                <div class="persona-content col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">RE-ORDERING</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Scented candles</h4>
                    <p>Billy has a stock pile of scented candles at home, so she can never run out of them. She has the favorites, but she is always open to new scent experiences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="persona-content col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">SHOPPING ONLINE</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Decision making</h4>
                    <p>When purchasing online, Billy either uses a laptop or a mobile device. She chooses candles based on a product maker, scent notes, price, and shipping charges.
                        <p>
                            <p>She gets frustrated when she can’t find products she loves online.</p>
                            <p>“I hate when I can’t find my favorite candles in stock.” </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/frustrated_shopper.png" alt="Illustration of a dissapointed women looking at the e-commerce shop and a scented candle product out of stock.">                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
