                    <h6 class="text-boja">ONLINE SECURITY</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Lack of trust</h4>
                    <p>Unfortunately, he doesn’t believe that retailers care about online security, although he is an avid technology user. He goes to Facebook and Instagram to keep up with his friends. He is an avid news reader. His favorite online publication
                        is Guardian. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
                <div class="persona-content col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
                    <h6 class="text-boja">UNFULLFILLED NEED</h6>
                    <h4 class="text-boja">Decision making</h4>
                    <p>Stewart is very busy with his work. He works as a certified trainer in a gym. That’s why he cherishes his time at home. Sometimes his flat has the uncomfortable musty odor, so he uses scented candles to combat the odor. He prefers
                        scents that remind him of cleanliness and purification.
                        <p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="img-fluid" src="illustrations/project1/gym.png" alt="Illustration of a trainer in a gym with weight in both hands and treadmill behind him."> </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center d-flex justify-content-between" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="3000" data-aos-easing="ease-in-out-cubic">
